main event: Observer Clarence Dillon reported hearing aircraft engines overhead on February 26, 1952, at Campbell Creek.
interesting points: Aircraft engines were heard at night with clear weather conditions., The sighting occurred at 11:50 PM C.S.T., The observer had a shocked emotional response to the sighting., The report is part of Project Blue Book, which documents various UFO sightings., There were later sightings documented, including multiple military evaluations in 1952.
